folder: Trotting Course Lane & Metropolitan Avenue, Queens, NY
original_title: Queens: Trotting Course Lane - Metropolitan Avenue
text:
Trotting Course Lane at the S.W. corner of Metropolitan Avenue, showing in two views the J. Vanderveer barns and house.  The barns seen in view No. 2 are located on the north side of Seventy-third Avenue and extend almost to Orville Place.  The house is directly in the street line of 72nd Avenue, near the first mentioned location.  In the background in view No. 1 is seen the elevated Long Island Railroad right of way.

April 1923.
Views 1 and 2

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
